{"tid":1683554,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【巴絲幫幫手入黎睇睇】2020意大利(北)之旅","createTime":"2019-10-30T16:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T04:20:30.000Z","uid":233963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"222a918dcd71eff6865dd242c7ff1d8fc93c59e9","tid":1683554,"uid":233963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:28:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/8 08:30 arrive - Milan </strong></span><br />\n(放低行李後去教堂同附近行下<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/9 Milan </strong></span><br />\n(15:30 San Siro Stadium 睇米蘭打呲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完去Navigli 飲下)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/10 Milan </strong></span><br />\n(諗住shopping然後周圍hea下)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/11 Milan 09:10 &gt; Florence SMN 11:04 </strong></span><br />\n(無plan去邊，行下景點)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/12 Florence </strong></span><br />\n(去中央廣場行下?)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/13 Florence SMN 08:20 &gt; Venezia S. Lucia 10:34 </strong></span><br />\n(Murano + Burano)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/14 Venezia </strong></span><br />\n(本島行下)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>2/15 Venezia </strong></span><br />\n(面具節，繼續留係本島睇遊行) 15:18 &gt; Milano Centrale 17:55，搭21:00機走<br />\n<br />\n想問下呢個行程應該唔算太趕?<br />\n上網都睇過大概每個地方有咩景點，都無乜話想趕景點，行到邊睇到邊都得<br />\n但有個問題... 完全唔知食乜好<br />\n除左Florence好似有個牛肚三文治一定要試<br />\n全程都好似食空氣睇景點就會飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位有無咩建議? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194bae3a62a4d57cab5a4d176999c147dc95e962","tid":1683554,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d70b2544e532324ac89e2cf34ce237ca09ed98a","tid":1683554,"uid":233963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262d81059f168e4475b474c5a8f6f7367e94d595","tid":1683554,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"今年我都去經過Florence 留3日 2夜<br />\n一日玩市中心<br />\n一日去Pisa"}]}